data.description: Check out this beautiful 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bath Townhome located in Huntly Park! This hidden gem is located in close proximity to everything in Orlando, centrally located to Shopping, Restaurants and Major Highways including I4. This updated unit is ready for a new home owner! Driving up to your unit you will have your own garage. Walk through your private, adorable courtyard into an open concept floorplan. You will find a kitchen featuring all stainless steel appliances and plenty of cabinets to store all your kitchen gadgets as well as a small breakfast nook in the kitchen area. The spacious living room and dining room have plenty of natural lighting! Not to mention a convenient half bath for the first floor. A sliding glass door leads you to a screened in lanai where you can enjoy your morning coffee or evening cocktail or just kick back and relax. As you walk upstairs, there is a small loft with a closet for the included washer & dryer. The primary bedroom features an en-suite with two closets. A second bedroom has access to the 2nd bathroom. This unit is just steps away from the community pool and clubhouse. HOA includes internet & cable with Disney Plus, night guard and lawn care. With a brand NEW tile roof less than 2 years, AC 2017, Newer exterior and interior paint, this townhome is ready to move right on in. Schedule your showing today as this home will not last long!
